# Data and run artifacts never belong in this repo.
# The package ships method code only; inputs and outputs stay local. Alias maps,
# vocabularies, and reference dumps are JSON, so JSON is excluded too; force-add
# an example file (git add -f) if one ever needs to ship.
/data/
/run/
/out/
/outputs/
*.jsonl
*.json
*.csv
*.parquet
*.png
*.pdf
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.npy
*.npz
